high_descs: walk to the coffeetable in the living room.
pick up the spoon from the center table.
Take the spoon to the kitchen and go by the sink.
Put the spoon in the sink, wash the spoon and then remove the spoon.
walk back over to the coffeetable.
Put the spoon on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Get the Spoon and put it on the CoffeeTable.

high_descs: Pick the spoon from the table.
Turn left go straight and take right to reach the sink.
Put the spoon on the sink and pour the water and clean the spoon.
Take the spoon turn right go straight reach in the coffeetable.
Place the cleaned spoon on top of the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Put the cleaned spoon on the top on the CoffeeTable.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the coffeetable in the living room.
Take the spoon from the table.
Turn around and go near the sink.
Put the spoon into the sink and wash it.
Then take it out and go near the coffeetable in the living room.
Put the spoon on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Placed the spoon on the CoffeeTable in the living room.
